{"tid":2214293,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中大女生黎明行動當日藏六角匙索帶被控 罪名不成立","createTime":"2020-09-23T07:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T10:53:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":73,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"88ebc91071286c385eb9098f126fc854e9b071a3","tid":2214293,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9732&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9qnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=80bd6d17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9732</a><br />\n<br />\n#觀塘裁判法院第八庭<br />\n#梁少玲裁判官 <br />\n#1111觀塘 #裁決<br />\n<br />\n梁 (21)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途使用<br />\n被控於2019年11月11日，在觀塘觀塘道近燈柱AB5425A，管有8條六角匙以及1包索帶，意圖將其作非法用途使用。<br />\n<br />\n背景：<br />\n去年11月11日網民發起「黎明行動」，號召全港「三罷」，多區均有堵路及警民衝突，事後多人被起訴。事隔近半年，案件於5月8日在觀塘裁判法院首度提堂，獲 #徐綺薇主任裁判官 批准以$1,000現金保釋，每週報到1次。同案原有另一名被告，僅涉藏有1包索帶被控管有工具罪，在7月21日獲准以簽保守行為方式處理，但控方堅持控告案中第二被告即21歲梁。梁不承認控罪，案件排期9月9日進行1天本地話審訊。<br />\n<br />\n✅速報：罪名不成立✅<br />\n❌訟費申請被拒❌<br />\n（詳情後補）"},{"pid":"d4916ab7aab59eff2412b574bf929b2a3382d1af","tid":2214293,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e8412f16d0fc4caa90e9ce6fff0d92d01d9344","tid":2214293,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4916ab7aab59eff2412b574bf929b2a3382d1af","tid":2214293,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:03:41.000Z","