1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:17:44.000Z","msg":"梁少玲嚟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"sor9ry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇錯保釋嗰段"},{"pid":"e23c084059be9d8d641ff3dfc2b5052dbe01e8b4","tid":2214293,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:25:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">大家要小心網絡安全，尤其是<ins>被咬過嘅手足</ins>，電話可能已經<span class=\"red\">被入侵</span>。港共可以用<span class=\"gold\">stingray</span><strong><span class=\"violet\">大規模監控</span></strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，<span class=\"red\">偷取IMSI(夠識別所有人)</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重私隱同網絡安全<span class=\"red\">被咬</span></strong>，<del>好大機會</del><span class=\"gold\"><ins><strong>包括</strong></ins></span><strong><span class=\"limegreen\">被綁架12人</span></strong>; 記得追蹤基爾巴: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/96327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/96327</a><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><ins><strong>請簽署制裁綁架12人嘅支那官員:<span class=\"x-small\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9qnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=e3848055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel</a><br />\n</span></ins></strong></span>[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107</a><b